  <h1 class="t-h1 hero__title t-balance">Three Layers of Awareness</h1>
  <p class="t-lead hero__lead t-pretty">Social conditioning, soul awareness, and embodied human life, and why confusing them can leave us ungrounded.</p>
</section>

